videos.headline: Williams strikes first with 37-yard UNC TD
videos.description: North Carolina's Antonio Williams bursts down the field for a 37-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Pickett gets Pitt on the board with 7-yard TD
videos.description: Kenny Pickett weaves through the North Carolina defense 7 yards for a Pittsburgh touchdown.

videos.headline: Elliott finds Carter for 31-yard UNC TD
